OL,6,FCourt documents show that Bryce
OL,7,FHodgson was handed a 16-week suspended
OL,8,Fjail term in July last year and put
OL,9,Funder supervision for 12 months after
OL,10,Fadmitting stalking.
OL,12,FThe 30-year-old was convicted of a
OL,13,Fcharge of stalking involving serious
OL,14,Falarm or distress for entering a
OL,15,Fwoman's bedroom without her consent,
OL,16,Ftexting her to demand she open her
OL,17,Fdoor, and describing vivid sexual
OL,18,Ffantasies to her, between January and
OL,19,FApril last year.
